text.section:
A member may purchase service credit for a period of employment:
not exceeding 10 years for out-of-state public school teaching service;
not exceeding 10 years for public or nonpublic school teaching service;
not exceeding 5 years for postsecondary school teaching service;
not exceeding 10 years for federal service or out-of-state service with a political subdivision; or
as an employee of a political subdivision of this State if the employee is not receiving retirement benefits from a political subdivision of the State for the same period of employment.
